high_descs: Turn left and go forward to the counter, then turn left to go to the counter above the dishwasher.
Pick up the fork on the counter in front of you.
Turn right and look up to the cabinets above the counter.
Open the leftmost cabinet and put the fork in the mug inside of the cabinet.
Pick up the mug from the cabinet.
Look down and then turn around and go straight, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the mug in the right sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with a fork in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the counter and walk to the counter with the dishwasher ahead.
Pick up the fork from the middle of the counter near the edge.
Turn right to face the counter with the tea kettle and look up at the cabinets.
Open the upper left cabinet and put the fork inside the white mug.
Pick up the mug with the fork inside the cabinet and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the mug with the fork inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a fork inside a sink.

high_descs: Turn left, and then make another left to walk to the dishwasher.
Take the fork from the counter above the dishwasher.
Turn right to face the cabinets above the microwave.
Put the fork in a white mug in the left-hand upper cabinet above the microwave.
Pick up the white mug with the fork in it.
Make a left to walk to the sink.
Put the fork and white mug in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork into a white mug to put into the sink.
